$ mp3 tools

Converting video and audio formats: → tools/ffmpeg.

Downloading videos from youtube and converting them to mp3: → tools/youtube-dl.

→ tools/mp3splt

→ tools/id3v2

→ tools/mp3info

`id3convert` can be used to strip *all* tags from an mp3 file: `id3convert -s files*.mp3`.
-
On → Linux/distributions/arch[Arch Linux], it needs to be installed with `sudo → Linux/distributions/arch/pacman -Sy id3lib`.

sa:
  → development/languages/Perl/modules[Perl modules] → development/languages/Perl/modules/MP3/Tag[MP3::Tag] and 
  → development/languages/Perl/modules/MP3/Info[MP3::Info]
